X-WR-CALNAME:Weaver line disruption
BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-04-16T21:45:00&endDate=2026-04-17T00:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nWEAVER LINE: Monday 13\, Tuesday 14\, Wednesday 15 and Thursday 16 April\, after 2245 each evening\, no service between Hackney Downs and Chingford. Replacement bus service L3 operates between Hackney Downs and Chingford via Clapton\, St James Street\, Walthamstow Central\, Wood Street and Highams Park. Last trains are at 2233 from Liverpool Street and 2255 from Chingford. The last three northbound buses leave Liverpool Street at 0014 0044 and 0114 and will also call at Bethnal Green\, Cambridge Heath and London Fields (Mare Street)
DTEND:20260417T002900Z
DTSTART:20260416T214500Z
SUMMARY:Weaver line: Part Closure
UID:1b21bd46-2d91-42c9-8a90-a848a4ca7565@1b21.org
END:VEVENT
